rows.label: tev056501_MSG0001
rows.name:
Ganglion is wreaking havoc all over Mira.
Many Nopon friends have been eaten![ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev056501_MSG0002
rows.name:
All this terror really puts kibosh on business.
Nopon cannot travel. Nopon cannot sell things.
And this mean Nopon cannot eat![ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev056501_MSG0003
rows.name:
If not for human friends, all Nopon might have gone
extinct.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev056501_MSG0004
rows.name:
Thank you, friend! Muimui is ready to work tuft off
in city to make fortune and recoup losses.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev056501_MSG0009
rows.name:
Unfair! Little brotherpon of Muimui, Moimoi, invented
all kinds of really useful machines for human friends![ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev056501_MSG0010
rows.name:
Who can live without pollen-orb radar, mmm?
And tuft fluffer VERY important before night on town!
But human friends not buy any of these wonder devices.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev056501_MSG0011
rows.name:
Soon Muimui and Moimoi will go out of business
and have to find landfill to dispose of surplus.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev056501_MSG0012
rows.name:
Does friend have any other get-rich-quick ideas?
...Or better yet, will friend purchase tuft fluffer in bulk?[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev056501_MSG0017
rows.name:
Guess what? Muimui and Moimoi joined BLADE
as Curators![ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev056501_MSG0018
rows.name:
Little brotherpon Moimoi invented amazing gadget
called Legen-dar to make work go faster.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev056501_MSG0019
rows.name:
Once Legen-dar is done, Muimui and Moimoi will
head out, find haul of goodies, and rake in cash![ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev056501_MSG0020
rows.name:
Friend is also BLADE, right? So friend should make
every effort to help Team Muimui out.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev056501_MSG1001
rows.name:
Muimui found thingy you call "meditation powder"
on third terrane of Talon Rock.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev056501_MSG1002
rows.name:
And on way home, Muimui passed through West
Janpath Plain and saw assassin springtails.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev056501_MSG1003
rows.name:
Muimui has been VERY busy establishing self as
top-shelf Curator for BLADE. Friend should be both
surprised and impressed.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev056501_MSG1004
rows.name:
And since Muimui was nice enough to share secret
information, friend should give major discount next
time Muimui needs help![ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev056501_MSG1009
rows.name:
All that work, and Muimui wind up with nothing
but legendary toy sword...[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev056501_MSG1010
rows.name: Mighty tuft of Muimui may never stand tall again...[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev056501_MSG1011
rows.name:
If Muimui ever cheers up, there might be new quest to
find real Sword of Legendaryness. But Muimui need
alone time right now...[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev056501_MSG2001
rows.name:
Muimui was searching Twin Arches in Oblivia when
Muimui stumbled on magical finding rod![ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev056501_MSG2002
rows.name:
And when Muimui tried dowsing with finding rod,
it showed cavern that contains ancient Nopon treasure
called "nopolith."[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev056501_MSG2003
rows.name:
Still no sign of Sword of Legendaryness, but Muimui
is proud of major breakthroughs as BLADE Curator.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev056501_MSG2004
rows.name:
Friend can say nice things about Muimui now.
Although major discount when friend does jobs for
Muimui would be more appreciated...[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev056501_MSG2009
rows.name:
Muimui and Moimoi are hard at work planning next
grand adventure. This time it will work out![ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev056501_MSG2010
rows.name:
Radar picked up some super legendary waves coming
from Sylvalum.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev056501_MSG2011
rows.name:
Muimui will tell friend when time is right.
In meantime, friend should train hard and make own
preparations for adventure.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev056501_MSG3001
rows.name:
Muimui has been very busy again. Located mega rare
item called penginion while passing Delusians
South Summit.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev056501_MSG3002
rows.name:
Oh, and Muimui also found rare insect called
snowy angelhair while swimming in Lake Ciel.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev056501_MSG3003
rows.name:
Muimui turning into total ace Curator these days.
Finding pretty much everything under sun EXCEPT
Sword of Legendaryness.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev056501_MSG3004
rows.name:
But just thinking about how many animals and insects
Muimui must find to keep food on table... Meh.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev056501_MSG3009
rows.name:
Muimui was all ready to teach Moimoi lesson,
but Moimoi manage to strike first due to increasingly
empty stomach of Muimui.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev056501_MSG3010
rows.name:
Only way to put bratty little brotherpon in place now
is to eatâ€”and to eat, Muimui must work extra hard
as BLADE.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev056501_MSG3011
rows.name:
*sigh* If only someone would send Muimui on
completely safe mission to catch ball mosquitoes
and earn 100,000 credits a pop...[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev056501_MSG3012
rows.name:
Instead Muimui keeps having to go up against
dangerous monsters and terrifying terrain.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev056501_MSG3013
rows.name:
Muimui really need to quit BLADE and find way to
make money without slowly killing self.[ST:wait ]
